snippet.title: Wallace & Gromit in The Grand Getaway - Official Release Date Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 20
snippet.description:
Wallace and Gromit in The Grand Getaway will be available on Meta Quest on December 7, 2023. Join Wallace and Gromit on a new adventure on a strange planet, and see puzzles and alien life in this latest trailer for the upcoming VR game.

#IGN #Gaming
